Aimee Kelly https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aimee_Kelly 0 Aimee Kelly is a British actress best known for her debut leading role in the feature film Sket, for which she was nominated Best British Newcomer at the London Film Festival Awards. Kelly also starred in CBBC's hit drama Wolfblood as Maddy Smith, for which she was nominated Best Children's performer by BAFTA.
